Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A Human male Jedi Knight served the Jedi Order during the Galactic War, and had some history with the Kaleesh Shakren san Jukii before san Jukii became the Sith Lord Razer. During the Battle of Corellia, the Jedi Knight spearheaded an aerial assault on the Imperial Garrison in Axial Park, and made straight for Razer, engaging him in lightsaber combat. The Jedi struck down Razer, but was killed in the moments following by the Imperial officers present in the room.
